    "rationale": "12 of 13 V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single below-required factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs required 3) is accepted given that the single load condition tested directly corresponds to the COU and is consistent with ASTM F1717 standard practice. All three primary QoIs pass quantitative acceptance criteria (E/uval < 1.96, relative difference < 10%). Model credibility is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision. Note: supplemental mesh-convergence evidence was appended post-signing without re-signing; this administrative gap should be remediated in the next package revision.",
